summary: Novak beat Jo-Wilfried Tsonga 6-3 7-5 6-4 and reached the third round of the Australian Open. Novak: “I thought I played pretty...
caption:
Novak beat Jo-Wilfried Tsonga 6-3 7-5 6-4 and reached the third round of the Australian Open.

Novak: “I thought I played pretty well for a set and a half, and I gained confidence in the third. It’s tough for Jo, who’s struggled with injuries the past year. But he’s always been a top player.”

(via BasiaID on Twitter, http://novakdjokovic.com/en/news/tennis/nole-moves-past-tsonga-into-third-round-of-australian-open/)
